---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const transcript = {
  title: 'Why Support the Stone Research Foundation',
  subtitle: 'Our Mission, Research Programs, and Impact',
  category: 'Foundation',
  duration: '1:30',
  relatedPage: '/donors',
  relatedVideo: '/videos#presentations',
};
---

<Layout title={transcript.title + " - Transcript"}>
  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="bg-stone-900 text-white py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <a href="/transcripts" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-stone-400 hover:text-white text-sm mb-6 transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/>
        </svg>
        All Transcripts
      </a>
      
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-xs px-3 py-1 bg-accent-500/20 text-accent-300 rounded-full">{transcript.category}</span>
        <span class="text-stone-400 text-sm">{transcript.duration}</span>
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="font-display text-display-sm md:text-display-md text-white mb-3">
        {transcript.title}
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-stone-300">{transcript.subtitle}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Transcript Content -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-accent-50 border-l-4 border-accent-500 p-6 mb-8 not-prose">
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600">
            <strong class="text-stone-900">The Mission:</strong> Accelerating healing, treating, preventing, 
            and curing arthritis through 30 years of developing science and techniques—now enhanced with 
            stem cells, hydrogels, growth factors, and personalized medicine.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="font-display text-xl text-stone-900 mb-4">Full Transcript</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-stone-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="timestamp-text">
            <span class="timestamp">[00:00]</span>
            At the Stone Research Foundation, we're dedicated to pushing forward the science, accelerating 
            healing, treating, preventing, and curing arthritis.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            We are teed up to solve a number of these problems with a <strong>30 year history</strong> of 
            developing the science and techniques.
          </p>
          
          <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200 p-5 rounded-sm my-6 not-prose">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-stone-900 mb-3">Current Research Focus Areas</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-stone-600">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Optimizing techniques with stem cells, hydrogels, and growth factors</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Personalized medicine research—testing each patient's tissues individually</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-500 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Programs to diminish patient atrophy after surgery</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <p class="timestamp-text">
            <span class="timestamp">[00:35]</span>
            New funding now to optimize those techniques by the addition of stem cells, hydrogels, and 
            other growth factors. Personalized medicine research where we can take each patient's tissues 
            and individually test them. And a number of other research programs that will help diminish the 
            patient's atrophy after surgery.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            We would love to have your support and the reason to donate to the Stone Research Foundation is 
            that we're <strong>lean, efficient, and quite leveraged</strong> in order to accomplish the goals 
            of solving arthritis and accelerating healing.
          </p>
          
          <p class="timestamp-text">
            <span class="timestamp">[01:00]</span>
            Your support will be well used to achieve those goals, and we very much appreciate thinking about 
            how we can keep you active—you, your children, and your grandchildren—<strong>playing to age 100</strong> 
            the sports you love.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-stone-900">
            Thank you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-accent-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h3 class="font-display text-display-sm text-white mb-4">Support Our Research</h3>
      <p class="text-accent-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Your contribution helps pioneer treatments that keep people active for life. Join our community 
        of supporters advancing the science of joint repair.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://stoneresearch.org/donate" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-accent-600 font-medium hover:bg-accent-50 transition-colors">
          Make a Gift Today
        </a>
        <a href="/donors" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white text-white font-medium hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          View Our Donors
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related Links -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-stone-50 border-t border-stone-200">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h3 class="font-display text-lg text-stone-900 mb-6">Learn More</h3>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <a href={transcript.relatedPage} class="p-5 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-sm hover:border-accent-400 transition-colors group">
          <span class="text-xs text-accent-600 uppercase tracking-wider">Community</span>
          <p class="font-display text-stone-900 group-hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors mt-1">Friends of the Foundation</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/research" class="p-5 bg-white border border-stone-200 rounded-sm hover:border-accent-400 transition-colors group">
          <span class="text-xs text-accent-600 uppercase tracking-wider">Science</span>
          <p class="font-display text-stone-900 group-hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors mt-1">Research Library</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .timestamp {
    @apply text-xs font-mono text-accent-600 bg-accent-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded mr-2;
  }
</style>
